istic length scales such as the roughness scale $z_0$, the LES grid\nscale $\\Delta$, and sub-grid scale (SGS) mixing length $C_s\\Delta$ are\nexamined. We also present LES results on moments of spanwise and wall-normal\nfluctuations of velocity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 May 2014 16:28:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Sep 2014 16:03:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-23"}
