ized wavenumber $k_{\\perp} \\rho_{i}$\nof order unity, the real and imaginary values of frequency become comparable\nand the growth rate maximizes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 May 2014 15:18:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
